                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-158-18501125 t18501125-158-punishment-142"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
